                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 159vc: This book is of the country of Sǝnqaṭa of Our Lady Mary. The one who stole it or took it by force or erased it will be excommunicated by the Authority of Peter and Paul, forever and ever, Amen and Amen. So be it, so be it.</q>
                           
